text: Breathe In is the second single released from the debut album of the same title by English singer-songwriter Lucie Silvas. "Breathe In" outpeaked her previous single "What You're Made Of" on the UK Singles Charts by one position, reaching number six. In Ireland, however, the song was not as successful as "What You're Made Of", stalling at number 34.
